Zain Companion Desktop Widget — Detailed Project Plan
=============================================

## 1. PROJECT VISION

A floating desktop widget (Windows) featuring a transparent morphing blob (bottom-right)
that expands into a horizontal iMessage-style chat bar on click. The blob is a
placeholder circle in early phases, evolving into a noise-driven organic shape in Phase 6.
Future phases add:
- Desktop awareness (widget reacts to what app you're using)
- LLM chat integration (Ollama/OpenAI/Anthropic/Gemini/DeepSeek)
- Sesame CSM voice output
- GPU-accelerated audio-reactive particle visualizations

