### Phase 4: LLM + TTS [DONE]
Chat works end-to-end with real AI models + Sesame CSM voice with low-latency streaming.
- Rust LLM proxy (5 providers): Ollama, OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, DeepSeek (fully implemented and verified)
- Streaming SSE parsing → token-by-token frontend events (fully implemented)
- Python sidecar: CSM model running on GPU (with offline fallback + pyarrow/triton fixes), JSONL IPC over stdin/stdout
- Rust sidecar manager: spawn, monitor, restart on crash (fully implemented)
- Audio playback pipeline: sidecar PCM chunks → Rust → Web Audio API (AudioWorklet)
- Token streaming animation + TTS sync (start TTS as soon as tokens arrive)
- CSM requires CUDA 12.4+ GPU + HuggingFace auth (sesame/csm-1b)
- Model download on first run (~4.15 GB CSM + ~2.3 GB Llama + mimi + silentcipher)
- Quantization options: FP16/INT8/INT4

